Variable.name: b1r
Variable.description: R magnetic field component generated from br and bp. b1r corrects the polarity of br which may have been flipped due to the anti-reconnection feature of advection. This value is essentially calculated bphi multiplying the sign of bp * br.

Variable.category: magnetic field vector components on r,phi,theta
Variable.name: b1phi
Variable.description: PHI magnetic field component generated from bphi and bp. b1phi corrects the polarity of bphi which may have been flipped due to the anti-reconnection feature of advection. This value is essentially calculated by multiplying the sign of bp * bphi.

Variable.name: b1theta
